The '''Mestský štadión''' is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Lučenec]], [[Slovakia]], currently used mostly for [[Association football|football]] matches. It is the home ground of [[FK LAFC Lučenec]] and holds a capacity of 5,000 people.
The stadium was damaged during the [[2010 Central European floods]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lucenec-online.sk/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=799&Itemid=61|title=Futbalový štadión LAFC Lučenec a Mestské kúpalisko pod vodou|work=[[Lučenec|lucenec-online.sk]]|date=7 June 2010|accessdate=16 September 2010|language=Slovak}}</ref>
